## NAND as NOT

NOT æ˜¯ä¸€ä¸ªå•è¾“å…¥çš„é€»è¾‘é—¨ï¼Œç”¨é€»è¾‘è¡¨è¾¾å¼ä¸ºï¼š$Y=\overline{a}$ ã€‚

å› ä¸º $a\cdot a = a$ æ‰€ä»¥ $Y = \overline{a\cdot a} = \overline{a}$

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/w1zd/image-hosting/main/img/2022/05/18/16-09-12-48e2df1cf8e864478f784e00ba475da8-NOT-GATE-7bc3cc.png)

```nand2tetris-hdl
/**
 * Not gate:
 * out = not in
 */

CHIP Not {
    IN in;
    OUT out;

    PARTS:
    // Put your code here:
    Nand(a = in, b = in, out = out);
}
```

## NAND as AND

AND Gate æ˜¯ä¸€ä¸ªä¸¤è¾“å…¥çš„é€»è¾‘é—¨ï¼Œç”¨é€»è¾‘è¡¨è¾¾å¼ä¸ºï¼š$Y=a\cdot b$, å…¶ä¸­ $a$ å’Œ $b$ åˆ†åˆ«æ˜¯è¾“å…¥çš„ä¸¤ä¸ªç«¯å£ã€‚

NAND Gate é€»è¾‘è¡¨è¾¾å¼ä¸ºï¼š$Y=\overline{a\cdot b}$ ï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬æƒ³è¦å¾—åˆ° $a\cdot b$ ï¼Œåªéœ€è¦å¯¹ $Y$ åšä¸€ä¸ªå–åæ“ä½œå³å¯ï¼Œå³ï¼š$Y' =\overline{\overline{a\cdot b}} = a\cdot b$

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/w1zd/image-hosting/main/img/2022/05/18/16-10-00-bebb701c23e2a068c6277fff14c22a7d-AND-GATE-a8a6a7.png)

```nand2tetris-hdl
/**
 * And gate:
 * out = a and b
 */

